## Executive Summary

This document provides comprehensive research on canvas/WebGL technologies for the MMS visualization system. The current implementation uses React Three Fiber (R3F) with InstancedMesh for rendering 60k+ tasks at 60fps. This research validates the technology choices and provides best practices for V1.0 optimization.

**Key Findings:**
